name: Project Identification
title: PROJECT
definition: Identifies the project number associated with this request.
usageNotes: Prohibited when RT field is “B”, otherwise optional.
fieldNotes: Use of this field includes: relating multiple ASR's, previously negotiated orders, etc.
The provider may initiate the project identification and provide this to the customer who will populate the field when submitting additional and/or supplement ASR Forms associated with this project.
